isfies a proposition iff it does not satisfy the negation of the proposition. ","docLink":"./Cslib/Logics/HML/Basic.html#Cslib.Logic.HML.neg_satisfies","kind":"theorem","line":127,"name":"Cslib.Logic.HML.neg_satisfies","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/b00648a4fe741981bb586a3cc845258ab1583f61/Cslib/Logics/HML/Basic.lean#L127-L131"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Logics/HML/Basic.html#Cslib.Logic.HML.satisfies_mem_denotation\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Logic</span>.<span class=\"name\">HML</span>.<span class=\"name\">satisfies_mem_denotation</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">State</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Label</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\">State</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Cslib/Logics/HML/Basic.html#Cslib.Logic.HML.Proposition\">Proposition</a> <span class=\"fn\">Label</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">lts</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/LTS/Basic.html#Cslib.LTS\">LTS</a> <span class=\"fn\">State</span> <span class=\"fn\">Label</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Cslib/Logics/HML/Basic.html#Cslib.Logic.HML.Satisfies\">Satisfies</a> <span class=\"fn\">lts</s